1. *Milosti* su pokazali prema ranjenima. (Mercy was shown to the wounded.)
2. Oni su zamolili za *milosti*. (They begged for mercy.)
3. Gospodin je pružio *milost*. (The Lord showed mercy.)
4. Uplašeni, tražili su *milosti*. (Frightened, they asked for mercy.)
5. Molimo za Božju *milost*. (We pray for God's mercy.)
6. Ponudili su *milosti* nevinima. (They offered mercy to the innocent.)